            <title>PROCEDURES AND INTERVALS</title>
            <para>The following inspection procedures are consistent with industry practice and are recommended as
                general guidelines for periodic service. Refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0200702">Figure 2</hotlnk>.
            </para>
            <figure id="f0200702" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g0200702" filename="../figg02/g0200702.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 2. Exploded View</caption>
            </figure>
            <para>Intervals of inspection or service are recommended for general or average vehicle use. It may be
                appropriate to increase the frequency of the intervals depending on the type of vehicle service.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
